{"id":57702,"date":"2024-07-08T16:47:49","date_gmt":"2024-07-08T11:17:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=57702"},"modified":"2024-07-12T18:02:26","modified_gmt":"2024-07-12T12:32:26","slug":"guide-to-bathroom-vanity-and-sink","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/guide-to-bathroom-vanity-and-sink\/","title":{"rendered":"The Ultimate Guide to Bathroom Vanity And Sink: Types and Styles"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Read our blog to find the latest bathroom vanity and sink ideas to make the most out of your space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vanities and sinks play an important role in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home design<\/a> but are often overlooked. Nevertheless, these elements are essential to creating a functional and stylish bathroom. In addition to storage, bathroom vanities and sinks play a crucial role in the overall design of your bathroom. This guide will explore the various types of bathroom vanity and sinks available in the market, their different styles, and why they are important.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Types of Bathroom Vanity<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Single Sink Unit for Small Bathroom Designs<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ideal for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/small-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">small bathrooms<\/a> or those with limited space, single-sink units are a popular choice for many homeowners. As the name suggests, they are designed with one sink and offer plenty of storage space for toiletries and other bathroom essentials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>It is designed with one sink.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Compact in size.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Available in various materials, finishes, and designs.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Ideal for small bathrooms.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>These units offer plenty of storage space for toiletries and other bathroom essentials.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They are cost-effective.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171020\/single-sink-unit-for-small-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Single sink unit with ample storage for small bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-57708\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171020\/single-sink-unit-for-small-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171020\/single-sink-unit-for-small-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171020\/single-sink-unit-for-small-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171020\/single-sink-unit-for-small-bathroom-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171020\/single-sink-unit-for-small-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Single vanities are perfect for homes with limited space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Double Vanities for Ample Storage<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/double-vanity-bathroom-ideas\/\">Double vanities<\/a> might be the perfect choice for the ample spaciousness if you have a larger bathroom. These vanities feature two sinks and ample storage space, making them ideal for couples or families.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Designed with two sinks<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Available in various materials, finishes, and designs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Most styles have additional features such as mirrors, lighting, and drawers.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>They are perfect for larger bathrooms.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Double vanities offer ample storage space.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Convenient for couples or families.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enhance the value of the property.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170931\/bathroom-double-vanities.jpg\" alt=\"Grey bathroom double vanities, convenient for couples or families\" class=\"wp-image-57703\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170931\/bathroom-double-vanities.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170931\/bathroom-double-vanities-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170931\/bathroom-double-vanities-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170931\/bathroom-double-vanities-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170931\/bathroom-double-vanities-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The honeycomb wall is the visually arresting feature of the space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Floating Bathroom Vanities for a Modern Style<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for a contemporary aesthetic for your bathroom, a floating bathroom vanity might be the way to go. These units are mounted to the wall, giving the illusion of floating above the ground. Often, they come in sleek and minimalist designs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Mounted to the wall.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Available in various materials, finishes, and designs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offers a decent amount of storage space.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Creates a modern and contemporary look.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ideal for small spaces.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Make cleaning easier.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offer under-vanity lighting.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171013\/floating-bathroom-vanity-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Floating bathroom vanity: sleek and minimalist designs\" class=\"wp-image-57707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171013\/floating-bathroom-vanity-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171013\/floating-bathroom-vanity-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171013\/floating-bathroom-vanity-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171013\/floating-bathroom-vanity-designs-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171013\/floating-bathroom-vanity-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Get extra floor space at no added cost<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pedestal Bathroom Sinks as a Classic Choice<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pedestal sinks are a classic choice for bathrooms. They are often found in traditional or vintage-style homes. They feature a stand-alone sink and offer a minimalist look that can open up your bathroom space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Stand-alone pedestal sink.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Variety of materials, finishes, and designs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Minimalist and open look.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Offer a classic and timeless look.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ideal for small spaces.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Easy maintenance.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enhances the resale value of the property.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170953\/bathroom-with-pedestal-sinks.jpg\" alt=\"Simple black bathroom with a pedestal sink design\" class=\"wp-image-57705\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170953\/bathroom-with-pedestal-sinks.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170953\/bathroom-with-pedestal-sinks-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170953\/bathroom-with-pedestal-sinks-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170953\/bathroom-with-pedestal-sinks-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12170953\/bathroom-with-pedestal-sinks-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A vintage vibe is easy with pedestal sinks<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Stylish bathroom vanity designs for your bedroom en-suite\" src=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/stylish-bathroom-vanity-designs-for-your-bedroom-en-suite.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall-Mounted Bathroom Vanity for Saving Space<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Wall-mounted vanities are another excellent option for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/elegant-modern-bathroom-design\/\">modern bathrooms<\/a>. They are attached to the wall, which creates more floor space and gives your bathroom a clean and streamlined look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Mounted directly onto the wall.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Immense choice is available in terms of materials, finishes, and designs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Open up floor space.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offer a streamlined look to the bathroom.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Perfect choice for those who crave a minimalist look.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Creates a modern ambience.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>This is a trending design.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It makes reselling your property easier.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Easy to clean.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offers additional storage space than a regular vanity.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171047\/wall-mounted-bathroom-vanity.jpg\" alt=\"Wall-mounted bathroom vanity for a clean and streamlined look\" class=\"wp-image-57711\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171047\/wall-mounted-bathroom-vanity.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171047\/wall-mounted-bathroom-vanity-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171047\/wall-mounted-bathroom-vanity-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171047\/wall-mounted-bathroom-vanity-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171047\/wall-mounted-bathroom-vanity-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Did you notice this popular design in all modern homes?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Different Types of Bathroom Styles<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Each style has its unique characteristics that cater to different buyer personas. When selecting a style for your bathroom furniture, it&#8217;s important to consider your personal taste, the overall style of your home, and your budget. Ultimately, your chosen style should enhance your bathroom&#8217;s overall look and functionality while reflecting eclectic taste. Here are some bathroom vanity styles to look out for!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Traditional Bathroom Vanity for a Classic Design<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Featuring classic designs, such as ornate detailing, antique finishes, and rich woods, traditional bathroom vanities are perfect for homeowners who want to create a warm and welcoming bathroom space with a timeless and classic look or simply for someone who prefers conventional or antique-inspired decor.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171028\/traditional-bathroom-vanity.jpg\" alt=\"Traditional bathroom vanity with intricate detailing, antique finish, and rich wood - creating a warm and inviting ambience\" class=\"wp-image-57709\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171028\/traditional-bathroom-vanity.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171028\/traditional-bathroom-vanity-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171028\/traditional-bathroom-vanity-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171028\/traditional-bathroom-vanity-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171028\/traditional-bathroom-vanity-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A quirky window makes the place look mod<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contemporary Bathroom Vanity for a Clean Look<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Contemporary bathroom vanity and sink offer sleek designs featuring clean lines, neutral colours, and modern materials such as glass and metal. They are ideal for homeowners who prefer a more streamlined look or those favouring a minimalistic and functional style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12175748\/contemporary-bathroom-vanity.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary bathroom vanity with double sink and mirror\" class=\"wp-image-57716\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12175748\/contemporary-bathroom-vanity.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12175748\/contemporary-bathroom-vanity-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12175748\/contemporary-bathroom-vanity-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12175748\/contemporary-bathroom-vanity-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12175748\/contemporary-bathroom-vanity-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The yellow cabinets make the space pop<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transitional Bathroom Vanity for a Blend of Design Styles<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Transitional bathroom vanity and sink blend traditional and contemporary design elements. They often feature classic shapes and finishes with modern materials and colours. This style is perfect for homeowners who prefer a versatile and adaptable style or for someone who loves to blend elements of traditional and modern decor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171037\/transitional-bathroom-vanity-unit.jpg\" alt=\"Transitional bathroom vanity unit in blue colour\" class=\"wp-image-57710\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171037\/transitional-bathroom-vanity-unit.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171037\/transitional-bathroom-vanity-unit-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171037\/transitional-bathroom-vanity-unit-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171037\/transitional-bathroom-vanity-unit-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/12171037\/transitional-bathroom-vanity-unit-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Blue cabinetry balances the starkness of the white bathroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bathroom vanity and sink are essential elements that help transform your bathroom into a functional, stylish space. A wide range of options are available to suit your needs and requirements.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking to kickstart your home interiors project? Connect with our expert designers at DesignCafe to get started right away!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ideas<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Design your personal oasis of comfort<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_actio